<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <title>Returns & Exchange | VASKA</title>
</head>
<body class="px-16 tracking-wide bg-[#FAF8F0] text-[#1e1e19] font-[Montserrat]">
    <%- include('partials/topbar') %>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto my-10 p-6 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Returns & Exchange Policy</h1>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">At VASKA, we strive to ensure customer satisfaction. If you are not happy with your purchase, you may request a return or exchange as per the policy outlined below.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">1. Eligibility for Returns & Exchanges</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
            <li>Items must be returned within 14 days of delivery.</li>
            <li>Products should be unused, unwashed, and in original packaging with tags attached.</li>
            <li>Final sale items, gift cards, and customized products are non-returnable.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">2. How to Initiate a Return</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
            <li>Log in to your VASKA account and navigate to the "My Orders" section.</li>
            <li>Select the item you wish to return and submit a return request.</li>
            <li>Once approved, you will receive a return shipping label.</li>
            <li>Pack the item securely and drop it at the nearest courier service.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">3. Refund Process</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Refunds are processed within 7-10 business days after the returned item has been received and inspected. The amount will be credited to the original payment method.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">4. Exchange Policy</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
            <li>Exchanges are available for size and color variations of the same item.</li>
            <li>If the requested variant is unavailable, a refund will be processed instead.</li>
            <li>Customers must return the original item before the exchange is dispatched.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Damaged or Incorrect Items</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">If you receive a damaged or incorrect product, please contact our customer support team within 48 hours of delivery to request a replacement.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">For further assistance regarding returns and exchanges, please <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 underline">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
